Worldstone: Bloodline Origins


Worldstone: Bloodline Origins is an RPG set in a universe full of strange creatures that you have to defeat. As you make your way through each area of the map, you'll be confronted by groups of enemies eager to take a piece out of you in a series of automatic battles. Of course, in each game, you can shape your strategy by employing different tactics as you see fit.


After selecting your warrior, you can dive into the action. The Worldstone: Bloodline Origins universe is populated by elves, orcs, humans, gods, and dwarves, all of whom you can either fight against or join forces with. In this sense, the tangle of relationships between characters encourages you to learn more about the story as it unfolds.


Keep in mind that as you play Worldstone: Bloodline Origins, you will have the option to visit the dungeons. Here, tons of characters remain prisoners, although you can try to save them by making certain decisions. To balance all the darkness, this game includes a dose of love, too, which means you can fight to survive without necessarily resorting to violence.


Worldstone: Bloodline Origins is an action-packed RPG where you fight against all creatures that coexist in this universe. By getting to know the characters, you can build relationships between them and escape from danger while also liberating humanity from evil forces.


